        "title": "Can you make an object serializable at runtime?",
        "body": "<p>Just like the title says, is there a way to check if an object is serializable, and if not, make it so at run time?<\/p>\n",
        "question_id": 3660567,
        "tags": [
            "java",
            "serialization",
            "runtime"
        ],
